snippet.textDisplay: This is my take: I love Coke Studio bangla, but I think this is a pop music video, not meant musicians but actors. Think Nasek Nasek or Bhober Pagol, it was the musicians who were highlighted, with the effort to sing or play instrument visible. In this video: it's the camera and the artists who are coming forward, not the singers. I hope Coke studio will return to original format.
